 three years of the H$\\alpha$\nintensity decline after the X-ray outbursts, a new circumstellar disk was being\nformed around the Be star after our 2013 observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Feb 2016 02:56:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-31"}
