e-free field\nextrapolation confirm the possibility of reconnection and the causal link\nbetween the magnetic systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Feb 2016 04:38:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-13"}
