erties of the fractional\nSchrodinger equation that are studied for the case of particle in one\ndimensional infinite potential well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Feb 2016 15:02:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-31"}
